<dl id="n12094n"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12094n">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12094n"> 94(n)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">I</font> Sits on coif to iron it</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Autrefois, les coiffes &eacute;taient bien plus &eacute;conomiques; elles &eacute;taient souvent en toile, comme dans le environs de Dinan. Elles co&ugrave;taient bien moins cher que les coiffes en dentelle d&apos;aujourd&apos;hui, on pouvait les laver et, comme m&apos;expliquait une bonne femme du pays gallo, pour les repasser, il n&apos;t avait &hellip; qu&apos;&agrave; s&apos;asseoir dessus. <br><font color="green">[In the old days the caps were cheaper; they were often made of canvas, as in the area around Dinan. They were a lot less costly than the caps in lace we see nowadays, they could be washed and, as a good lady of the Gallo region told me, <mark>if they needed ironing, you could just sit on them</mark>.]</font> <small> <a name="RDBR" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#RDBR"><cite title="source">Revue de Bretagne</cite></a> (1904) 235</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
